title: TODO ? Ask Claude for more?
pid: 06d9b467-71a0-4290-9558-d0e776a679b5
body: |2-
  Find link triples in which each member is delicious.
  It is valid for part of a triple to be ?,
  if that is the most delicious considering also word labels.

  Hey Claude please fill this out so the graph is pretty,
  by collecting from data/real/public?
  You'll have to translate ideas into subgraphs --
  often an idea is an arrowlike triple,
  but as the higher data in the following org-mode bucket show,
  it's not necessarily even naturally expressible as a graph.
